You are walking along the first floor landing of the farm house, by the top of a flight of stairs leading back down to the ground floor. The hallway here has several doors running along it, but only one if them has any kind of indication where it leads: Roughly to the south east, a 'bathroom' sign hangs on the door. There are other doors, all identical, varnished wood, to the west, east and south of the landing. You can also go back down the stairs to the ground floor from here.
