Each end table is made from a dark, cherry coloured wood, expertly carpented from what appears to be one single solid piece of tree. No drawers or other compartments are visible.
On one of the tables, separate from it entirely, is a freshly made wooden handle. It's not attached to anything at all. It looks like someone here was prepairing to repair a piece of furniture, but left the handle here.
